  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.3">
<l>irakka maṉattō ṭeriyaṇai</l>
<l>yarakku meḻukumok kumiva</l>
<l>ḷirakka meḻīritaṟ keṉceykē</l>
<l>ṉarakka ṉilaṅkaiceṟ ṟīrukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This one resembles sealing wax</l>
<l>on a bed of flame, with a mind merciful</l>
<l>towards you who subdued Laṅkā [and its] king.</l>
<l>You who don’t rise to mercy, what shall I do about it?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
